additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Concentrated chicken Sock (64%) [water, vegetables (carrot, leek, garlic), chicken (2.2%) (fat, meat), parsley, pepper], salt, vegetable oil, sugar, yeast extract (contains barley), flavours, thickeners (xanthan gum, locust bean gum), burnt sugar, maltodextrin, rosemary extract, natural colour (carotene). Contains naturally occurring glutamates.

additionalProperty.name: Allergen
additionalProperty.value: May Be Present Sesame Seeds, May Be Present Milk, May Be Present Crustacea, May Be Present Peanuts, Contains Cereals Containing Gluten, May Be Present Egg

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: 1 Pot makes 2 cups At Continental we believe that food should be full of flavour and that what you get out is only as good as what you put in. Continental Superb Stock, Flavour to feel good about.
